{"tid":2024053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[畢業論文問卷求幫忙] 反修例運動國際線問卷","createTime":"2020-05-19T11:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T09:41:13.000Z","uid":355266,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59a6a1c37b0fea52dc7f890abf4a6cd6013dd20b","tid":2024053,"uid":355266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"各位手足，唔知可唔可以幫手做份有關反修例運動國際線嘅問卷， master畢業論文用的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去問卷右上角可以揀語言<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=6de0908c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast</a><br />\n<br />\n份paper主要係從社會心理學角度出發，想搵吓有啲乜嘢因素驅使人去參與國際線嘅行動，而「國際線」究竟會唔會對參加者/非參加者有啲咩影響/轉變。得出嚟個result係諗住思考吓「國際線」可以點走落去，如果份嘢寫得正正常常，第時有機會可能share個結果出嚟大家一齊討論吓。<br />\n<br />\n為咗保障各位，份問卷係匿名的，亦set好唔會記錄IP等等任何可以識別到受訪者的個人資料。份問卷全部都係選擇題，除咗問你大概參加過幾多次唔同類型嘅活動之外，唔會問到你參加嘅任何細節，希望可以令大家放心啲。當然，保護自己好緊要，做到一半想唔做，可以隨時退出。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果做完份問卷覺得可以的話，大家都可以推吓同埋share俾身邊親朋好友去做。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫幫手，感謝! 如有任何意見，都歡迎留底個comment! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送上J圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=6WPBHWKfRDEAX9iR2Rz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=4fafe93b886c8d60a498fa620fd42f0a&amp;oe=5EC74D08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26_nc_ohc%3D6WPBHWKfRDEAX9iR2Rz%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D4fafe93b886c8d60a498fa620fd42f0a%26oe%3D5EC74D08&h=9603792c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69236045_1250300895094290_8992316132203429888_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=eYRXi_6Cg2AAX9qgfN1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=ec1887588d762c0f3de1c1ba5dd018b5&amp;oe=5EE43CAB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69236045_1250300895094290_8992316132203429888_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DeYRXi_6Cg2AAX9qgfN1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3Dec1887588d762c0f3de1c1ba5dd018b5%26oe%3D5EE43CAB&h=9c5e8745&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f47a9dfd7a4bf4837a5da07ced18d4893bfb74e3","tid":2024053,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"建議你真係擺j圖會好d<br />\ndone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a34167b348c8436e78d4c3d7f50d6b82aa8ac9b","tid":2024053,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"Done as well<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9814470e3ee1681ddb419da5cef22dd53c4459","tid":2024053,"uid":355266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f47a9dfd7a4bf4837a5da07ced18d4893bfb74e3","tid":2024053,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"建議你真係擺j圖會好d<br />\ndone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打!!<br />\n見其他問卷PO都係真J圖，之前出post要俾教授望吓個post所以唔敢擺，大家要的我補返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0efd2203f80ba410ee2217381d81857b4ccdee","tid":2024053,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f9814470e3ee1681ddb419da5cef22dd53c4459","tid":2024053,"uid":355266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f47a9dfd7a4bf4837a5da07ced18d4893bfb74e3","tid":2024053,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score